# This directory holds pending git-sync requests written by harness agents
# (which run in a sandbox that cannot run git directly). The launchd daemon
# `com.harness.gitrunner` picks up each `.json` file in here, runs the git
# commit + push outside the sandbox, and removes the marker on success.
#
# Marker file format (JSON):
#   {
#     "agent": "trader" | "news" | "research" | "manual",
#     "message": "[trader 2026-06-02] ...",
#     "created_at": "2026-06-02T16:05:00-07:00",
#     "branch": "main"
#   }
#
# Do NOT commit this directory's marker files to git. .gitignore handles that.
